## Summary of Keyboard Accessibility Test Results

### 1. ARIA Attributes on Search Input
- **Element**: `<input type="search" id="emoji-mart-search-1" placeholder="Search">`
- **Explicit ARIA role**: **NONE** (no `role="combobox"`)
- **Implicit ARIA role**: `searchbox` (from `type="search"`)
- **aria-autocomplete**: **NONE** - Missing
- **aria-controls**: **NONE** - Missing
- **aria-haspopup**: **NONE** - Missing
- **aria-label**: **NONE** (name derived from `<label>` element)
- **aria-labelledby**: **NONE**
- **Accessible name**: "Search" (from associated `<label class="emoji-mart-sr-only">`)

### 2. ARIA Attributes on Emoji List Container
- **Element**: `<div class="emoji-mart-scroll">`
- **ARIA role**: **NONE** (implicit `generic` role)
- **aria-label**: **NONE** - Missing (no accessible name for the emoji list)
- **aria-live**: **NONE** - Missing

### 3. ARIA Attributes on Emoji Items
- **Element**: `<span class="emoji-mart-emoji">` (or similar)
- **ARIA role**: **NONE**
- **aria-label**: **NONE**
- **tabIndex**: **-1** (not in tab order)

### 4. Keyboard Navigation Test
- **Arrow keys from search input (no filter)**: ❌ **FAILS** - pressing Down/Right/Left/Up arrow keys does NOT navigate to any emoji
- **Arrow keys from search input (with "smile" filter)**: ❌ **FAILS** - pressing Down/Right/Left arrow keys does NOT navigate to filtered emoji results
- **Arrow keys after clicking an emoji**: ❌ **FAILS** - pressing Right arrow after clicking an emoji does NOT navigate to the next emoji

### 5. Visual Issues Observed
- The emoji picker shows a "Search Results" section when filtering works correctly (functional filter)
- The emoji preview at the bottom updates on mouse click (functional click interaction)
- No visual focus indicator appears on any emoji when arrow keys are pressed

Based on all these findings, the emoji picker has **significant keyboard accessibility issues**:
1. **No combobox ARIA role** on the search input (should be `role="combobox"` with `aria-autocomplete="list"`, `aria-controls`, `aria-expanded`)
2. **No ARIA role** on the emoji list container (should be `role="listbox"` or `role="grid"`)
3. **No accessible name** on the emoji list (should have `aria-label`)
4. **Arrow key navigation completely non-functional** - cannot navigate between emojis using keyboard
5. **No keyboard focus indicators** on emoji items

